    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it handles beautifully and looks great too. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a new home where it'll be appreciated just as much. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
