      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a specialized ionic current knock-sensing system to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending torque to a variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including the replacement of rod bearings with treated shells and updated throttle actuators to ensure valvetrain reliability. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematic integrity, with the MacPherson strut front and five-link rear suspension providing precise damping and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. A driver-focused example with all major mechanical systems operating at peak performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable performance. No major mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
