      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains balanced and communicative, benefiting from a recent suspension refresh with Bilstein dampers. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity remains high, delivering a linear power band and sharp throttle response. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
